ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisAppointment of PAUL ATERMAN of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Head Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designation of PAUL ATERMAN to be Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Head Office), effective March 9, 2015.
